{"tid":2065814,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"和支那不同調 咸濕菜：支那北京新疫情病例已破百","createTime":"2020-06-16T00:16:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-16T01:43:14.000Z","uid":32511,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"5dc69b3f9d9598e36ebe0a1747602e62d18227bb","tid":2065814,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T00:16:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3198838\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3198838&d=UliE8fwpyfwMZiesMcCM7jv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=ab2fcb18\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3198838&h=bcc3cfef\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3198838</a>"},{"pid":"6b6f8e5dbfbe28bf7d4377376ea74eb5e9fe245d","tid":2065814,"uid":197157,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T00:17:29.000Z","msg":"習敗敗係咪唔記得課金啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40866b1170213c8b9bf2e6c1e2138dff7167ec0c","tid":2065814,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T00:19:24.000Z","msg":"沒事兒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18dbc9b8ca2d2f34776d797734ab1ed919eab302","tid":2065814,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T00:19:41.000Z","msg":"〔編譯黃靖媗／綜合報導〕中國北京市武漢肺炎（新型冠狀病毒病，COVID-19）疫情重燃。世界衛生組織（WHO）15日記者會中指出，北京市爆發這一波新疫情已有逾百起確診病例，並警告，許多國家受武漢肺炎疫情影響，中斷了對其他流感的監控。<br />\n<br />\n世衛組織秘書長譚德塞（Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus）於記者會中表示，中國上週回報北京市出現新的感染病例，已經有超過100起確診病例，這波疫情的起源與規模仍在調查中。<br />\n<br />\nWHO：近期新增疫情集中在美洲與南亞<br />\n全球疫情部分，世衛組織已收到回報超過780萬起確診病例、43萬死亡，譚德塞指出，超過兩個月才累積前10萬起確診病例，但過去兩週，幾乎每天都會新增超過10萬起確診病例，近期新增的病例大約75%集中於美洲、南亞的10個國家，非洲、東歐、中亞、中東的確診病例數也在逐漸上升中。<br />\n<br />\n譚德塞也於記者會中提到，由於武漢肺炎疫情導致交通中斷、實驗室負擔過重，人力資源與物資補給皆被重新分配，許多國家中止了對流感的監測，各國流感資訊的共享也因為武漢肺炎疫情急遽下滑，與過去3年相比，今年全球的流感樣本數量大幅減少，送到WHO合作中心的樣本數量少了62%。這可能會造成短期與長期的影響，部分國家恐因此喪失檢驗流感、回報具有大流行潛力病毒的能力。"},{"pid":"339aed17068483b40e92a3ae3b0dcf23ac8d8f4e","tid":2065814,"uid":125168,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T00:21:06.000Z","msg":"佢講破百都係想維穩姐，邊止咁少"},{"pid":"0c87349b8ae6f54f2940ae118701e68b2aa78dff","tid":2065814,"uid":321837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5dc69b3f9d9598e36ebe0a1747602e62d18227bb","tid":2065814,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T00:16:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3198838\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3198838&d=UliE8fwpyfwMZiesMcCM7jv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=ab2fcb18\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3198838&h=bcc3cfef\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3198838</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T00:23:12.000Z","msg":"中共都話係九十幾, <br />\n譚仔家下話破百係咩意思? 101? 定又嚟百幾萬?"},{"pid":"73be5dc87f5bd8c1815ad7e0af1a0467b17f5ffc","tid":2065814,"uid":321837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"339aed17068483b40e92a3ae3b0dcf23ac8d8f4e","tid":2065814,"uid":125168,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T00:21:06.000Z","msg":"佢講破百都係想維穩姐，邊止咁少"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T00:27:02.000Z","msg":"亦有可能根本就無,純粹一箭數鵰<br />\n刮幾十萬人嘅隔離費用. 200X14日X人數, 金!<br />\n話係疫情,咁咩會咩法未拖住先囉,睇下出面人點反應先再決定點玩.<br />\n仲有可能為第二次傳播作準備. <br />\n你真係唔知係咩事嘅啵.<br />\n因為果到係無新聞/言論等自由架, 司法亦非獨立........."},{"pid":"7bd03b6b58d38248d43f989e68c45a4426b5eef9","tid":2065814,"uid":274149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T00:32:44.000Z","msg":"今個月會費比遲咗"},{"pid":"36c1b21aed7978ceb012b6190f5b8309e2a26adb","tid":2065814,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T00:37:26.000Z","msg":"Give me more money"},{"pid":"b9144d789372e